    <h4 class="my-5">Here are the top 10 technologies to learn in 2023:</h4>
    <div class="stack mb-5">

      <h5>Artificial intelligence (AI) and machine learning (ML)</h5>
      <p>
        Artificial intelligence is already being used in many application around the world from small startups to tech
        giants like google, Microsoft
        Tesla etc. From self driving cars to predictive analytics AI have made it possible.
        <br>

        Machine Learning is a subset of Artificial Intelligence that focuses on building models from data instead of
        designing them manually.

        <br>
        In 2023 the demand for qualified professionals in the this growing day by day as more companies working on
        on AI and Machine Learning.

      <div class="">
        Prerequisites for learning Artificial Intelligence (AI) and machine learning (ML) include solid proficiency in
        any one programming languages
        like Python (recommended), R, LISP, Java, and sufficient knowledge of mathematical concepts such as statistics,
        linear algebra, calcular, matrices, probablity.

      </div>

